{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setEmails:","title":"setEmails:"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"emails","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings. Each must be a valid email format.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"emails"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Associates multiple email addresses with the current device for omnichannel"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"email campaigns. This is useful when users have multiple email addresses"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(work, personal, etc.) and want to receive communications on all of them."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All provided emails will be linked to the same device and user ID,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"enabling unified targeting across all addresses."}]},{"text":"Example","level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Register multiple emails from user profile:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class UserProfileManager {","","    func syncEmailsFromProfile(_ profile: UserProfile) {","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primary = profile.primaryEmail {","            emails.append(primary)","        }","        if let secondary = profile.secondaryEmail {","            emails.append(secondary)","        }","        if let work = profile.workEmail {","            emails.append(work)","        }","","        guard !emails.isEmpty else { return }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmails(emails)","","        \/\/ Update tags with email count","        Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","            \"email_count\": emails.count,","            \"has_work_email\": profile.workEmail != nil,","            \"has_multiple_emails\": emails.count > 1","        ])","    }","}"]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setEmails:":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setEmails:","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setemails:","abstract":[{"text":"Registers multiple email addresses associated with the current user.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setEmails:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setEmails:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setEmails:"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","abstract":[],"role":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}]}}}